Cancel Model Creation

You can cancel model creation before Einstein finishes creating it. Canceling a model interrupts Einstein data analysis and abandons any model elements created after you clicked Create Model.

Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

To cancel model creation, click the Cancel button.

Clicking the button halts the creation of a new model (or a new model version) and returns you to the Home page.
